Package org.age.mag.hazelcast.listeners

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistributedObjectListenerImpl
    Listener for distributed objects.
    LifecycleListenerImpl
    Logs information about changes in lifecycle service.
    MembershipListenerImpl
    Listens for members addition or deletion, passing this information to cluster manager to update list of connected members.
    MessageListenerImpl
    Logs every received message.
    NodeDescriptorListener
    Handles information about node descriptor changes passing it to ClusterManager.
    NodeStatusListener
    Handles information about node status changes, passing it to ClusterManager.
    PartitionLostListenerImpl
    Logs every lost partition.
    TopologyConfigListener
    Handles information about master, topology type and graph changes.
    WorkerConfigListener  
    WorkerStateListener
    Handles given events and updates node worker state by passing it to ClusterManager.
